snippet.title: Lisa MarieTTC
snippet.description:
Hi and welcome to my channel where you will find our journey of how we became parents via a friend & known egg donor, along with our infertility struggles before that all took place. Now that Gemma is a toddler, I do reviews, unboxing, hauls and lots of activities with her and homeschooling related things.
Most of my videos are mommy related and just showing what works for us in our lives. Thanks for stopping by and I hope you subscribe to stay up to date on what were doing and whats new with our little family!
Stay in touch on my facebook page @lisamariettc
I snap most days.... Snapchat @lisamariettc
For questions or inquiries about reviewing your product or doing an unboxing,  please email me directly at: LisasVlog@gmail.com
